## Government of Canada Design System

This software incorporates design patterns and guidelines from the Government 
of Canada Design System (https://design.canada.ca/), which is available under 
the Open Government Licence - Canada (https://open.canada.ca/en/open-government-licence-canada).

The GC Design System components included in this software are provided for 
compliance with Canadian government digital standards and are subject to the 
terms of the Open Government Licence - Canada in addition to the MIT License above.

