## Privacy & Data Residency

This software is designed to support Canadian data residency requirements and
compliance with the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents
Act (PIPEDA). Users are responsible for ensuring their use of this software
complies with applicable privacy laws and regulations.

## Accessibility Statement

This software is designed to meet Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.2
Level AAA standards. We are committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people
with disabilities and continually improving the user experience for everyone.

If you encounter any accessibility barriers, please report them to:
accessibility@eva-sovereign.ca

